# Conquer Utilities

This directory contains the **conqrast** map visualization tool for the Conquer game.

## About conqrast

**conqrast** creates graphical maps of Conquer games on bitmap display systems.

### Original Author
- Written by Richard Caley in 1989  
- Original email: rjc@uk.ac.ed.aipna (historical)

